    "collapsible_content_NNPzfc": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_UqUbNX": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "HOW CAN A T-SHIRT LAST A LIFETIME?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>We don’t cut corners. Evertee is built with premium, sustainable materials designed to outlive your wardrobe. And if it doesn’t? We’ll replace it. Simple as that.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_fmCMR3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "WHY SHOULD I PAY MORE FOR A T-SHIRT?",
            "icon": "price_tag",
            "row_content": "<p>Because it’s the <em>only</em> t-shirt you’ll ever need. While you’re busy buying dozens of fast-fashion t-shirts every year, Evertee is saving you <strong>money</strong>, time, and the planet. Over a lifetime, it’s a motherflippin' bargain.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_WQJC9K": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "WHAT IF MY T-SHIRT GETS DAMAGED?",
            "icon": "recycle",
            "row_content": "<p>Don’t sweat it. Tear? Hole? Weird stain you don’t want to talk about? Send it back, and we’ll replace it. We’ve got your back for life.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_67nEph": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "HOW DOES EVERTEE HELP SAVE THE PLANET?",
            "icon": "plant",
            "row_content": "<p>By ditching fast fashion. Our t-shirt replaces <strong>80+ disposable tees</strong>, saves <strong>216,000 liters of water</strong>, and prevents <strong>hundreds of kilos of CO₂ emissions</strong>. One t-shirt, one massive impact.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_g3tTQJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "WHAT MAKES EVERTEE SO DAMN COMFORTABLE?",
            "icon": "shirt",
            "row_content": "<p>It’s crafted from ethically sourced, ridiculously soft, natural fibres. It feels so good, you’ll wonder why you ever wore anything else. Go ahead, try it—your skin will thank you.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_LbVnQH": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "WHAT'S THE CATCH?",
            "icon": "eye",
            "row_content": "<p>There isn’t one. You get a lifetime guarantee, unmatched quality, and the satisfaction of telling fast fashion to eff<em> off. No catches, no bull </em>—just a damn good t-shirt.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
